      <title>电梯还是楼梯？研究发现，你的选择可以延长寿命</title>
      <link>https://npr.org/sections/health-shots/2024/04/29/1247532191/longevity-stairs-climbing-exercise-heart-disease</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新的研究表明，与不习惯爬楼梯的人相比，有爬楼梯习惯的人死于心脏病的可能性更低。爬楼梯的人的寿命也略有延长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://npr.org/sections/health-shots/2024/04/29/1247532191/longevity-stairs-climbing-exercise-heart-disease</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 09:01:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
